This time around, BBI seems a pre-emptive deal aimed at power sharing post-2022 General Election. Following the proceedings of the Building Bridges Initiative, one thing coming out is that it is an ODM-led campaign. They have immersed themselves in pursuit of the ‘handshake’ benefits with gusto.
The term ‘crying louder than the bereaved comes to mind’ as ODM remains right in the heart of the BBI campaigns than even Jubilee Party, who co-own the handshake. As incumbents, Jubilee Party should be singing the loudest on BBI and handshake but for some peculiar reasons, it is measured and divided.



