ODM’s support of the BBI throws up the idea of nusu mkate once more. This time around, BBI seems a pre-emptive deal aimed at power sharing post-2022 General Election. Which makes the ‘handshake even more suspicious. It’s the worst idea ever mooted if its intention is to create another nusu mkate government.



