His sacrifices as he pushed against the single party State will be etched in the history of Kenya for posterity. The 2010 Constitution that we are now proud of could not have been realised without his sacrifice, in-put and resolve. He remains one of the heroes of what came to be known as the 2nd Liberation of Kenya.
The current Constitution recently celebrated its 10th year. It has not hit puberty yet let alone being considered a fully grown and sickly adult requiring treatment. He is now leading a brigade through BBI to reverse all the democratic gains he singularly brought to the country.



